OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 31 MAY
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1998FSky Scottish ceases
OL,7,Fbroadcasting, after just over 18 months
OL,8,Fon air. The channel was a joint venture
OL,9,Fbetween BSkyB and ITV franchise-holder
OL,10,FSMG plc. It was aimed at Scottish
OL,11,Fpeople who lived outside Scotland who
OL,12,Fwould not otherwise have been able to
OL,13,Freceive local programming from STV,
OL,14,FGrampian Television and BBC Scotland.
OL,15,FSky Scottish broadcast hours were 6pm -
OL,16,F8pm.
